OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'I watch my back': Spike in
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FBBC journalists living in  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fexile                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The number of BBC World Service        
OL,6, journalists working in exile is        
OL,7, estimated to have nearly doubled, to   
OL,8, 310, since 2020.                       
OL,10,FThe figures, released for the first    
OL,11,Ftime ahead of World Press Freedom Day, 
OL,12,Freflect press crackdowns in Russia,    
OL,13,FAfghanistan, and Ethiopia.             
OL,15,FJournalists from other countries,      
OL,16,Fincluding Iran, have lived abroad for  
OL,17,Fmore than a decade.                    
OL,19,FMany face jail sentences, death threats
OL,20,Fand harassment, both on and offline.   
